PN,30901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782398899
OL,3,CWomen who blame brain tumours on
OL,4,Ccontraceptive jab fight for change
OL,6,FA group of women who believe they have
OL,7,Fdeveloped brain tumours as a result of
OL,8,Flong-term use of a contraceptive
OL,9,Finjection are calling for a UK-wide
OL,10,Freview of the drug.
OL,12,FThey took their fight for answers,
OL,13,Fawareness and accountability to
OL,14,FHolyrood on Wednesday morning and met
OL,15,Fwith a cross-party group of Members of
OL,16,FScottish Parliament.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782398899
OL,3,CWomen who blame brain tumours on
OL,4,Ccontraceptive jab fight for change
OL,6,FThere were tears and supportive hand
OL,7,Fsqueezes as they each described some
OL,8,Fof the devastating health impacts they
OL,9,Fhave suffered and their desire to
OL,10,Fensure no other woman goes through the
OL,11,Fsame.
OL,13,FTheir lawyers demanded action on what
OL,14,Fthey described as a medical scandal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782398899
OL,3,CWomen who blame brain tumours on
OL,4,Ccontraceptive jab fight for change
OL,6,FDepo-Provera - also available in a
OL,7,Fself-administered form known as Sayana
OL,8,FPress - has been linked to a
OL,9,Fsignificant increase in the risk of
OL,10,Fdeveloping a type of brain tumour
OL,11,Fcalled a meningioma. Current research
OL,12,Fsuggests the overall risk remains low.
OL,14,FAlthough the tumours are usually
OL,15,Fbenign, they can have devastating
OL,16,Fconsequences. Depending on their
OL,17,Flocation, they may cause persistent
OL,18,Fheadaches, visual disturbances,
OL,19,Fhearing loss, balance problems,
OL,20,Fseizures and cognitive changes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782398899
OL,3,CWomen who blame brain tumours on
OL,4,Ccontraceptive jab fight for change
OL,6,FMany women have to undergo major brain
OL,7,Fsurgery and/or gruelling radiotherapy
OL,8,Fto treat them.
OL,10,FThe manufacturer Pfizer - in
OL,11,Fcollaboration with the UK's medicines
OL,12,Fregulator, the MHRA - updated the
OL,13,Fpatient leaflet with a brain tumour
OL,14,Fwarning in 2024.
OL,16,FThe campaign in Scotland is being led
OL,17,Fby Tammy Croston from Fife, who was
OL,18,Fone of the first women in UK to speak
OL,19,Fout about her experience in an
OL,20,Finterview with ITV News earlier this
OL,21,Fyear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782398899
OL,3,CWomen who blame brain tumours on
OL,4,Ccontraceptive jab fight for change
OL,6,FShe told a cross-party group of
OL,7,FMembers of Scottish Parliament (MSPs)
OL,8,Fthat she would never have taken Depo-
OL,9,F Provera if she had known it could
OL,10,Fcause brain tumours. Tammy ultimately
OL,11,Flost the use of her right eye
OL,12,Ffollowing the surgery she underwent.
OL,14,F"It's affected not just me but
OL,15,Fhundreds if not thousands of women
OL,16,Facross the UK." she said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782398899
OL,3,CWomen who blame brain tumours on
OL,4,Ccontraceptive jab fight for change
OL,6,F"This is not about taking
OL,7,Fcontraceptive choices away from women,
OL,8,Fit's about keeping women safe and
OL,9,Fmaking sure they're fully informed
OL,10,Fabout what they're putting into their
OL,11,Fbodies.
OL,13,F"If you're on the depo for two years
OL,14,Fare you likely to develop a
OL,15,Fmeningioma? Probably not, but lots of
OL,16,Fus have been on it for 10, 20, 30
OL,17,Fyears and that is why the signs are
OL,18,Fnow coming out. We want to stop the
OL,19,Fnext generation from having to go
OL,20,Fthrough what we have been through."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782398899
OL,3,CWomen who blame brain tumours on
OL,4,Ccontraceptive jab fight for change
OL,6,FIf you or anyone you know has been
OL,7,Faffected by this issue or has a story
OL,8,Fto share, you can get in touch by
OL,9,Femailing: investigations@itv.co.uk
OL,11,FNicola Mackay from Portmahoak was on
OL,12,FDepo-Provera for 23 years until she
OL,13,Fhad five seizures last February.
OL,15,FShe has since gone on to have brain
OL,16,Fsurgery and radiotherapy, but she has
OL,17,Fbeen left with seizures.
OL,19,F"I was just in hospital two weeks ago
OL,20,Fwith two seizures," she said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782398899
OL,3,CWomen who blame brain tumours on
OL,4,Ccontraceptive jab fight for change
OL,6,F"They're watching and waiting and
OL,7,Fscanning me every six months, because
OL,8,FI do have three tumours ` one has been
OL,9,Fremoved and I've got two remaining
OL,10,Ftumours left in my brain. It'll be
OL,11,Flifelong, and it's just changed my
OL,12,Flife dramatically for the worse."
OL,14,FSonja Ferrier from Forfar in Angus had
OL,15,Fto give up training as a driving
OL,16,Finstructor when she started having
OL,17,Fproblems with her vision. She was
OL,18,Feventually diagnosed with multiple
OL,19,Fmeningiomas, one was pressing on her
OL,20,Foptic nerve.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782398899
OL,3,CWomen who blame brain tumours on
OL,4,Ccontraceptive jab fight for change
OL,6,FShe said said: "I was told that I may
OL,7,Fhave even more but because they're
OL,8,Fslow growing, it may take longer
OL,9,Fbefore they start showing.
OL,11,F"I was on this drug for 30 odd years,
OL,12,FI was still on it after my
OL,13,Fradiotherapy and only stopped it when
OL,14,Fmy doctor advised me it was feeding
OL,15,Fthe meningiomas and undermining the
OL,16,Fradiotherapy."
OL,18,FThe women who attended the meeting at
OL,19,FHolyrood are just a handful of the
OL,20,Fmany more affected right across the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782398899
OL,3,CWomen who blame brain tumours on
OL,4,Ccontraceptive jab fight for change
OL,6,FLaw firm Austen Hays, which is
OL,7,Fexploring compensation claims for
OL,8,Fwomen in England and Wales, says it is
OL,9,Fnow representing more than 350 women.
OL,11,FScottish law firm Thompson's is
OL,12,Frepresenting around 70 women in
OL,13,FScotland, though says more are getting
OL,14,Fin touch every week.
OL,16,FPartner Patrick McGuire said: "This is
OL,17,Fa scandal and every woman here today
OL,18,Fhas been a victim of that scandal.
OL,19,FThey've been belittled and they've
OL,20,Fbeen ignored.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782398899
OL,3,CWomen who blame brain tumours on
OL,4,Ccontraceptive jab fight for change
OL,6,F"This is a scandal that runs very
OL,7,Fdeep, it's decades long, the women
OL,8,Fhave so many questions, they want
OL,9,Fanswers and they want to ensure
OL,10,Flessons are learnt.
OL,12,F"The only way that can be achieved is
OL,13,Ffor a full UK wide public inquiry. We
OL,14,Fexpect every single MSP of every
OL,15,Fcolour to get behind this and make
OL,16,Fthat demand of the UK government."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782398899
OL,3,CWomen who blame brain tumours on
OL,4,Ccontraceptive jab fight for change
OL,6,FJackie Bailey, MSP for Dunbarton and
OL,7,FScottish Labours Health and Social
OL,8,FCare spokesperson, hosted the meeting.
OL,9,FIt was also attended by
OL,10,Frepresentatives from the SNP, the
OL,11,FScottish Conservatives and the
OL,12,FScottish Greens.
OL,14,FAll were in agreement that action
OL,15,Fshould be taken to ensure better
OL,16,Feducation among the public and
OL,17,Fhealthcare professionals, and that
OL,18,Fproper support should be put in place
OL,19,Ffor women who have been long-term
OL,20,Fusers of Depo-Provera and are seeking
OL,21,Fmedical advice and treatment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782398899
OL,3,CWomen who blame brain tumours on
OL,4,Ccontraceptive jab fight for change
OL,6,FSpeaking after the meeting, Jackie
OL,7,FBailey MSP said she was supportive of
OL,8,Fthe calls for the UK-wide public
OL,9,Finquiry, after hearing what she
OL,10,Fdescribed as really emotional
OL,11,Ftestimony.
OL,13,F"I think it's clear we need to
OL,14,Funderstand why we got to this position
OL,15,Fand I'm supportive of the call for an
OL,16,Finquiry but I'm also very pragmatic
OL,17,Fabout what we can do now," she said.
OL,19,F"Making sure that any contraception is
OL,20,Fsafe absolutely has to be the number
OL,21,Fone priority of any government.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782398899
OL,3,CWomen who blame brain tumours on
OL,4,Ccontraceptive jab fight for change
OL,6,F"I would like the Scottish government
OL,7,Fitself to take a rapid review and
OL,8,Fprovide advice both to women and to
OL,9,Fclinicians."
OL,11,FIn a statement Scotland's Public
OL,12,FHealth Minister Maree Todd said: "I
OL,13,Fhave the utmost sympathy for women who
OL,14,Fbelieve they have been harmed by Depo
OL,15,FProvera, and I will be meeting some of
OL,16,Fthe women next week to hear first-hand
OL,17,Fof their experiences.
OL,19,F"However, I cannot comment on matters
OL,20,Fwhich may be subject to legal action.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782398899
OL,3,CWomen who blame brain tumours on
OL,4,Ccontraceptive jab fight for change
OL,6,F"The regulation of medicines is
OL,7,Freserved to the UK Government, meaning
OL,8,Fany further investigation into Depo
OL,9,FProvera would be a matter for it the
OL,10,FMedicines and Healthcare products
OL,11,FRegulatory Agency (MHRA) to consider."
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FIt would be up to the UK government to
OL,19,Frespond to calls for a public inquiry.
OL,20,FThe Department of Health and Social
OL,21,FCare has been approached for comment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30916
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782398899
OL,3,CWomen who blame brain tumours on
OL,4,Ccontraceptive jab fight for change
OL,6,FIn a statement the UK's medicine's
OL,7,Fregulator the MHRA said: "Patient
OL,8,Fsafety is our top priority.
OL,10,F"For the majority of people, the
OL,11,Fbenefits of Depo-Provera outweighs the
OL,12,Frisks, but we advise anyone with any
OL,13,Fconcerns to speak with their GP,
OL,14,Fpharmacist, or contraceptive provider.
OL,16,F"In line with usual processes, the
OL,17,Fneed for further regulatory action
OL,18,Fwill be considered, should significant
OL,19,Fnew information be identified."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30917
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782398899
OL,3,CWomen who blame brain tumours on
OL,4,Ccontraceptive jab fight for change
OL,6,FThe manufacturer Pfizer said: "Patient
OL,7,Fsafety is our top priority. We conduct
OL,8,Frigorous and continuous monitoring of
OL,9,Fall our medicines in collaboration
OL,10,Fwith health authorities around the
OL,11,Fglobe.
OL,13,F"Depo-Provera has been approved in
OL,14,Fmore than 60 countries over the last
OL,15,F30 years, has a well-established
OL,16,Fefficacy and safety profile and has
OL,17,Fbeen a treatment option for millions
OL,18,Fof patients during that time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30918
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782398899
OL,3,CWomen who blame brain tumours on
OL,4,Ccontraceptive jab fight for change
OL,6,F"People should talk to their doctor,
OL,7,Fpharmacist or nurse if they have any
OL,8,Fconcerns or experience any side
OL,9,Feffects."
OL,11,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,12,Four political experts are across all
OL,13,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,14,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/18
